Name: Average resolution time for 'Completed + Cancelled'
Metric: The average of the duration between the start of the case and activity 'Completed + Cancelled'

Name: Average time difference between 'Completed + Cancelled' and 'Accepted + In Progress'
Metric: The average of the duration between activity 'Accepted + In Progress' and activity 'Completed + Cancelled'

Name: Total duration of incidents before reaching 'Completed + Cancelled'
Metric: The sum of the duration between the start of the case and activity 'Completed + Cancelled'

Name: Minimum time to reach 'Completed + Cancelled' from 'Queued + Awaiting Assignment'
Metric: The minimum of the duration between activity 'Queued + Awaiting Assignment' and activity 'Completed + Cancelled'

Name: Average time from 'Completed + In Call' to 'Completed + Cancelled'
Metric: The average of the duration between activity 'Completed + In Call' and activity 'Completed + Cancelled'

Name: Total time from 'Accepted + In Progress' to 'Completed + Cancelled'
Metric: The sum of the duration between activity 'Accepted + In Progress' and activity 'Completed + Cancelled'

Name: Minimum time from 'Completed + Resolved' to 'Completed + Cancelled'
Metric: The minimum of the duration between activity 'Completed + Resolved' and activity 'Completed + Cancelled'

Name: Average duration of 'Completed + Cancelled' incidents in the VINST system
Metric: The average of the duration between the start of the case and activity 'Completed + Cancelled'

Name: Average time from 'Completed + Cancelled' to the next activity in the process
Metric: The average of the duration between activity Completed + Cancelled and the end of the case

Name: Total number of transitions from 'Accepted + Wait - User' to 'Completed + Cancelled'
Metric: The sum of the duration between activity 'Accepted + Wait - User' and activity 'Completed + Cancelled'
